  "design_notes": "This easy chart features an elegant, rhythmic progression starting with sparse half and quarter-note taps in the S0 intro to introduce the BPM comfortable pacing. During the S3 main drop, the density comfortably increases to include steady quarters with a very select number of expressive holds on key vocal transitions and downbeat accent jumps. The break (S2) and outro (S4) are kept gentle with sparse downbeats to prevent dead pauses, aligning beautifully with the energy curve.",
